<span class="token constant">F</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>n<span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token constant">F</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>n <span class="token operator">-</span> <span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token operator">+</span> <span class="token constant">F</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>n <span class="token operator">-</span> <span class="token number">2</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span>，其中 n <span class="token operator">></span> <span class="token number">1</span>
</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><p>给你 n ，请计算 F(n) 。</p>
