输出：<span class="token number">2</span>
解释：最大的子集是 <span class="token punctuation">{</span><span class="token string">"0"</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token string">"1"</span><span class="token punctuation">}</span> ，所以答案是 <span class="token number">2</span> 。
</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><blockquote>
